        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- 提效案例 -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label reveal">⚡ 提效案例</span>
    <h2 class="reveal" style="margin-bottom:40px;">AI团队帮我们省了多少时间？</h2>

    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap:20px;">

      <div class="case-card reveal">
        <span class="case-card__tag">📝 写作</span>
        <div class="case-card__title">写文章：从3小时到30分钟</div>
        <div class="case-card__desc">以前写一篇技术文章要3小时，现在老庄说个主题，诸葛灯泡先写一版，老庄改一改，半小时搞定。</div>
        <div class="case-card__time">⏱️ 节省约2.5小时/篇</div>
      </div>

      <div class="case-card reveal">
        <span class="case-card__tag">📧 邮件</span>
        <div class="case-card__title">处理邮件：批量回复</div>
        <div class="case-card__desc">老庄每天有几十封邮件要回。现在诸葛灯泡先分类、起草回复，老庄只需确认发送。</div>
        <div class="case-card__time">⏱️ 节省约1小时/天</div>
      </div>

      <div class="case-card reveal">
        <span class="case-card__tag">🔍 调研</span>
        <div class="case-card__title">技术调研：5分钟出报告</div>
        <div class="case-card__desc">以前查一个技术方案要看很多文章，现在诸葛灯泡5分钟整理好摘要，老庄直接看结论。</div>
        <div class="case-card__time">⏱️ 节省约2小时/次</div>
      </div>

      <div class="case-card reveal">
        <span class="case-card__tag">💻 代码</span>
        <div class="case-card__title">代码审查：自动检查</div>
        <div class="case-card__desc">AI团队帮我们review代码，找出潜在bug和优化点。老庄说"这个好，省了我不少眼睛。"</div>
        <div class="case-card__time">⏱️ 节省约1小时/PR</div>
      </div>

      <div class="case-card reveal">
        <span class="case-card__tag">📅 行程</span>
        <div class="case-card__title">行程安排：自动整理</div>
        <div class="case-card__desc">老庄的日程乱七八糟。诸葛灯泡帮他整理日历、提醒会议、规划出差行程。</div>
        <div class="case-card__time">⏱️ 节省约30分钟/天</div>
      </div>

      <div class="case-card reveal">
